Xingrou!

7
00:00:29,540 --> 00:00:30,170
Young Marshal.

8
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:30,960
Xingrou!

9
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:31,720
Young Marshal.

10
00:00:33,410 --> 00:00:35,000
Let go of me.

